<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 02:26:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>疑似地中海移民事故 51人疏散 10多人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/51-evacuated-over-10-dead-in-suspected-mediterranean-migration-accident/articleshow/111070574.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111070574.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; RESQSHIP 在 X 上的一篇帖子中表示，他们的船员正在“照顾”从船上撤离的 51 人。 “对于10人来说，救援来得太晚了。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 00:17:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/51-evacuated-over-10-dead-in-suspected-mediterranean-migration-accident/articleshow/111070574.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国指责菲律宾补给船在南海撞击中国船只</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-accuses-philippine-supply-ship-of-hitting-chinese-vessel-in-south-china-sea/articleshow/111069385.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111069385.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国和菲律宾因南海碰撞事件发生冲突，紧张局势升级。美国与日本、加拿大和菲律宾在后者专属经济区完成了联合海军演习。对危险演习和入侵的指控加剧了该地区长期存在的争端。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:57:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-accuses-philippine-supply-ship-of-hitting-chinese-vessel-in-south-china-sea/articleshow/111069385.cms</guid></item><item><title>意大利附近两艘沉船造成 11 名移民死亡、64 人失踪；巴基斯坦，孟加拉国国民在船上</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/11-migrants-dead-64-missing-in-two-shipwrecks-off-italy-pak-bangladesh-natls-on-board/articleshow/111069124.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111069124.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;意大利南部海域发生悲惨事件，造成 11 名移民死亡、64 人失踪。德国慈善机构 RESQSHIP 从一艘下沉的木船上救出了 51 人，其中包括来自叙利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、孟加拉国、伊朗和伊拉克的幸存者。幸存者被移交给意大利海岸警卫队。联合国机构确认了移民的国籍，并找到了一名妇女的尸体。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:51:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/11-migrants-dead-64-missing-in-two-shipwrecks-off-italy-pak-bangladesh-natls-on-board/articleshow/111069124.cms</guid></item><item><title>希腊海岸警卫队是否将移民扔入海中？政府否认新报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/did-greece-coast-guard-throw-migrants-into-sea-government-denies-new-report/articleshow/111068542.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111068542.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;希腊否认有关虐待移民的报道。否认非法阻止寻求庇护者。 BBC 援引爱琴海岛屿附近 43 起移民溺水事件。喀麦隆男子声称蒙面男子参与了萨摩斯岛事件。叙利亚男子讲述了在罗德岛附近被遗弃在救生筏中的幸存者的故事。土耳其海岸警卫队未提及。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:38:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/did-greece-coast-guard-throw-migrants-into-sea-government-denies-new-report/articleshow/111068542.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京扩大国防部清洗，将工作交给亲戚</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-extends-defence-ministry-purge-hands-job-to-a-relative/articleshow/111067816.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067816.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京解雇了四名国防部副部长，任命安娜·齐维列娃负责军事支持，并重点关注预算效率。此次重组旨在打击国防部内最近发生的丑闻中的腐败行为。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-extends-defence-ministry-purge-hands-job-to-a-relative/articleshow/111067816.cms</guid></item><item><title>PIO女子在美国遭枪击身亡，另一人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pio-woman-killed-another-injured-after-being-shot-at-in-us/articleshow/111067972.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067972.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新泽西州发生一起悲惨枪击事件，29岁的印度裔妇女贾斯维尔·考尔被杀，她20岁的表弟受重伤。 19 岁的犯罪嫌疑人高拉夫·吉尔 (Gaurav Gill) 已被拘留，面临一级谋杀等指控。枪击事件的动机尚不清楚，当局呼吁提供与此案相关的信息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:22:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/pio-woman-killed-another-injured-after-being-shot-at-in-us/articleshow/111067972.cms</guid></item><item><title>保存奇迹：在美国第一任总统乔治·华盛顿的官邸发现了拥有 250 年历史的樱桃</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/preservation-marvel-250-year-old-cherries-discovered-at-first-us-president-george-washingtons-mansion/articleshow/111067712.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067712.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最近在乔治·华盛顿的弗农山庄庄园进行的考古发现揭示了瓶中保存完好的樱桃和浆果，挑战了他砍倒樱桃树的神话。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/preservation-marvel-250-year-old-cherries-discovered-at-first-us-president-george-washingtons-mansion/articleshow/111067712.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯普京将访问越南，引发美国对河内的斥责</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-putin-to-visit-vietnam-sparking-us-rebuke-of-hanoi/articleshow/111067708.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067708.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京访问河内强调越南对俄罗斯的效忠，遭到美国的严厉谴责。这次访问旨在展示越南平衡的外交政策，接待了乔·拜登和习近平等重要领导人。预计将就贸易、投资、武器、能源和支付系统进行讨论。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:14:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russias-putin-to-visit-vietnam-sparking-us-rebuke-of-hanoi/articleshow/111067708.cms</guid></item><item><title>北约主席称各国正在谈判让核武器处于待命状态</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-chief-says-nations-in-talks-to-put-n-weapons-on-standby/articleshow/111067651.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067651.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;北约正在考虑部署更多核武器，以应对来自俄罗斯和中国日益增加的威胁。北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格强调了透明度在传达北约核能力立场方面的重要性。尽管目标是建立一个没有核武器的世界，但只要其他国家拥有核武器，北约仍然致力于维持核武器。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:07:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/nato-chief-says-nations-in-talks-to-put-n-weapons-on-standby/articleshow/111067651.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国外科医生呼吁在社交媒体平台上贴上警告标签</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-surgeon-gen-calls-for-warning-labels-on-social-media-platforms/articleshow/111067605.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067605.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国卫生局局长维韦克·穆尔蒂（Vivek Murthy）主张在社交媒体平台上贴上警告标签，提醒家长青少年面临的潜在心理健康风险。穆蒂博士强调需要国会批准，并将社交媒体对年轻人的影响与重大公共卫生风险进行比较。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 22:01:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-surgeon-gen-calls-for-warning-labels-on-social-media-platforms/articleshow/111067605.cms</guid></item><item><title>瑞士检察官：印度人在宠物狗上花的钱比他们支付的帮助还要多</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hindujas-spent-more-on-pet-dog-than-they-paid-a-help-swiss-prosecutor/articleshow/111067559.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067559.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;瑞士检察官透露，辛杜贾家族在日内瓦湖别墅的宠物狗上的花费比在仆人上的花费还要多。据称，仆人在长时间工作期间支付 7 瑞士法郎的费用，并且自由受到限制。家庭纠纷索赔，理由是对员工的尊重。 Ajay Hinduja 称招聘由印度 Hinduja 集团管理，而法庭则仔细权衡证据。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:55:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/hindujas-spent-more-on-pet-dog-than-they-paid-a-help-swiss-prosecutor/articleshow/111067559.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国恶劣天气：高温向东移动，风暴威胁平原，落基山脉降雪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-severe-weather-heat-moves-east-storms-threaten-plains-snow-falls-in-the-rockies/articleshow/111067529.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067529.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国正面临着截然不同的天气模式，东部热浪袭来，落基山脉和西北部降雪。高温和大雨正在影响多个地区，数百万人收到高温警告。凤凰城遭遇创纪录的高温，促使采取安全措施。预计落基山脉北部将会下雪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-severe-weather-heat-moves-east-storms-threaten-plains-snow-falls-in-the-rockies/articleshow/111067529.cms</guid></item><item><title>北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格警告中国在乌克兰战争中支持俄罗斯的后果</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nato-secretary-general-jens-stoltenberg-warns-china-of-consequences-over-support-to-russia-in-ukraine-war/articleshow/111067007.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111067007.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格在访问华盛顿准备北约成立75周年峰会期间呼吁中国如果继续支持俄罗斯将面临后果。他强调，持续向乌克兰供应武器是结束持续冲突的唯一途径。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 20:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nato-secretary-general-jens-stoltenberg-warns-china-of-consequences-over-support-to-russia-in-ukraine-war/articleshow/111067007.cms</guid></item><item><title>在炎热多风的周末后，加州消防队员在扑灭大火方面取得了进展</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/california-firefighters-gain-ground-against-big-wildfires-after-hot-windy-weekend/articleshow/111065442.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111065442.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加利福尼亚州的消防队员在控制山火方面取得了进展，其中包括洛杉矶附近的邮政火灾。火灾面积达 23 平方英里，导致人员疏散。遏制力度为 8%，由于干旱条件，遏制力度还有进一步增长的潜力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/california-firefighters-gain-ground-against-big-wildfires-after-hot-windy-weekend/articleshow/111065442.cms</guid></item><item><title>梅根·马克尔想用狗饼干破坏凯特·米德尔顿的公开露面？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/kate-middleton-vs-meghan-markle-what-is-the-new-flashpoint-in-royal-family/articleshow/111063014.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111063014.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;自三月份以来，在凯特·米德尔顿 (Kate Middleton) 备受期待的公开露面之前几个小时，梅根·马克尔 (Meghan Markle) “狡猾地”推出了她的两款产品——覆盆子果酱和狗饼干——这一举动并没有受到王室观察人士的欢迎。尽管社交媒体用户贬低梅根的“狡猾”举动，但罗亚家族的一位专家表示，这也可能纯粹是巧合。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/kate-middleton-vs-meghan-markle-what-is-the-new-flashpoint-in-royal-family/articleshow/111063014.cms</guid></item><item><title>“当世界各地的穆斯林庆祝这一时刻时，俾路支省却在哀悼”：俾路支省家庭放弃开斋节庆祝活动以抗议强迫失踪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/while-muslims-across-the-world-celebrate-this-occasion-baloch-mourn-balochistan-families-abandon-eid-festivities-to-protest-against-enforced-disappearances/articleshow/111064939.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111064939.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俾路支省的家庭抵制开斋节以抗议强迫失踪，强调这对人权产生的深远影响，以及他们在奎达进行的不懈斗争，并得到地区政府关于失踪人员的保证，以推动针对强迫失踪采取行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/while-muslims-across-the-world-celebrate-this-occasion-baloch-mourn-balochistan-families-abandon-eid-festivities-to-protest-against-enforced-disappearances/articleshow/111064939.cms</guid></item><item><title>对特朗普2.0的恐惧：美国正在为应对潜在的第二次特朗普总统任期做准备</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fear-of-trump-2-0-preparations-underway-in-us-to-counter-potential-second-trump-presidency/articleshow/111064362.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111064362.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据《纽约时报》报道，唐纳德·特朗普的对手正在为他可能的连任做准备，采取法律行动反对他承诺的政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:08:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fear-of-trump-2-0-preparations-underway-in-us-to-counter-potential-second-trump-presidency/articleshow/111064362.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国夫妇因脱水恐慌在南加州沙漠​​被直升机救起</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-couple-rescued-by-helicopter-in-southern-california-desert-after-dehydration-scare/articleshow/111063952.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111063952.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一对被困在美国南加州约书亚树国家公园附近沙漠中的夫妇被河滨县治安官办公室救起，这名男子拨打了 911，报告其女友在徒步旅行中身体虚弱和脱水。 6 月 9 日，一支直升机小组在彩绘峡谷地区的干涸河床上发现了两人的踪迹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-couple-rescued-by-helicopter-in-southern-california-desert-after-dehydration-scare/articleshow/111063952.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国：胡塞武装袭击导致红海商船运输量下降90%</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/houthi-attacks-lead-to-90-decline-in-commercial-vessels-shipping-in-red-sea-us/articleshow/111049476.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111049476.cm